data.description: Welcome Home! This great location offers 1.2 acres and comfortable living. The open floor plan, flooded with natural light, features a spacious living room, Formal dining, two bedrooms and a full bathroom on the main level. The lower level offers a cozy family room and 2 bonus rooms that the new buyers could convert into official bedrooms after adding an egress window in each room. Instant equity! Brand new LVP, Carpet & Fresh paint throughout the home. Brand New Roof in 2023. Enjoy picturesque surroundings. Don't miss the chance to call this beautiful property your new home!
